{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Visibility"], "type": "title", "extent": [90, 105], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [105, 168], "text": ["Shows/hides primitives in the 3D viewer and UV editor."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [168, 464], "text": ["This operator changes the visibility of primitives (such as polygons) in\nthe viewer. It is similar to the nondestructive hide/show functionality\nin other modeling and illustration software. You can use this node to\nhide part of a model to get it \"out of the way\" while you work on\nanother part."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [464, 697], "text": ["Unlike other packages where you use a menu command to hide polygons and\nthen another to show them again, the Visibility SOP is part of the\nnetwork, so to show hidden polygons again you can just delete or bypass\nthe Visibility node."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [697, 839], "text": ["Because this operator only changes the visibility of the primitives,\ntopology, point numbers, primitive numbers, and so on are not affected."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [845, 955], "text": ["This operator does not affect rendering. It only changes the\n    visibility of primitives in the viewer."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "note", "extent": [839, 845]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [290, 343], "text": ["Select the primitives to hide or expose."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [441, 535], "text": ["You can edit the visibility settings in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, "."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/visibility", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/visibility"}, {"text": ["Visibility"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/visibility", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/visibility"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["Model"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."], "extent": [343, 441], "blevel": 6, "type": "ord"}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [535, 585], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/shelf/visibility.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/shelf/visibility.png"}]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [585, 790], "text": ["This tool does not delete the selected area, it merely hides it. This is useful because the remaining points do not change as they would if the area was deleted and it does not affect rendering. "]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [790, 1050], "text": ["You can get primitives to reappear by choosing Expose Primitives in the ", {"text": ["Action"], "type": "ui"}, " drop-down menu in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, " or by deleting or bypassing the ", {"text": ["visibility"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/visibility", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/visibility"}, " node in the ", {"text": ["network editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/network", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/network"}, "."]}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Using Visibility"], "extent": [255, 290], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "includeme"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1017, 1063], "text": ["A subset of primitives to hide/show."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Group"], "role": "item", "extent": [1006, 1017], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1103, 1158], "text": ["Sets the visibility of the input primitives."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [1183, 1236], "text": ["Hide the input primitives in the viewer."]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [1158, 1183], "text": ["Hide primitives"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [1263, 1316], "text": ["Show the input primitives in the viewer."]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [1236, 1263], "text": ["Expose primitives"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Action"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/action"}, "extent": [1063, 1075], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1359, 1497], "text": ["Controls whether this operator hides/shows the input primitives,\n        or all other primitives ", {"text": ["except"], "type": "em"}, " the input primitives."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [1526, 1570], "text": ["Hide/show the input primitives."]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [1497, 1526], "text": ["Selected primitives"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [1603, 1647], "text": ["Hide/show all other primitives."]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [1570, 1603], "text": ["Non-selected primitives"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Apply to"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/applyto"}, "extent": [1316, 1330], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1703, 1913], "text": ["Applies the changes to visibility without changing the current\n        visibility of unaffected input primitives. If this option is\n        off, all visibility is reset according to the options above."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1913, 2174], "text": ["For example, say primitive 2 was hidden in the input geometry\n        and this node hides primitive 5. If this option is on, both\n        primitives 2 and 5 will be hidden in the output. If this option\n        is off, only primitive 5 will be hidden."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Apply Cumulatively"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/cumulative"}, "extent": [1647, 1671], "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [994, 1006], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2183, 2205], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/lod", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/lod"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [2174, 2183], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "title": ["Visibility"], "summary": ["Shows/hides primitives in the 3D viewer and UV editor."], "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "view, util", "namespace": null, "internal": "visibility", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/visibility"}, "included": ["/shelf/visibility"], "type": "root"}